==English==

===Etymology===
Alternation (due to {{m|en|give}}) of {{inh|en|enm|foryiven}}, {{m|enm|forȝiven}}, from {{inh|en|ang|forġiefan|t=to forgive, give up, provide}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*fragebaną|t=to give away; give up; release; forgive}}, equivalent to {{af|en|for-|give}}. Cognate with {{cog|sco|forgeve}}, {{m|sco|forgif}}, {{m|sco|forgie|t=to forgive}}, {{cog|fy|ferjaan|t=to forgive}}, {{cog|nl|vergeven|t=to forgive}}, {{cog|de|vergeben|t=to forgive}}, {{cog|is|fyrirgefa|t=to forgive}}.

